{"sections":[],"metadata":{"platforms":[{"introducedAt":"2017.01.20","name":"Brunow"}],"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"title":"The Inside Shows Through"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A good façade must be thick enough to mask what lies beneath it. It adds bulk and in my mind unnecessary weight. A bad façade barely hides what is below it and causes a feeling of disease in the minds of those who see it as they try to tie the inside and outside together."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Not using a façade only works if what is inside is what you want to show the world."}]}]}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/07-20-the-inside-shows-through"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/07-20-the-inside-shows-through"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-07-20T22:22:32-05:00"}],"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2016":{"url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2016","title":"2016","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016","abstract":[]},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"url":"\/documentation\/brunow","title":"Brunow","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he."}]},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive","title":"Archive","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","abstract":[{"text":"All posts","type":"text"}]}}}